    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention to be roadworthy again. The engine has a persistent knock and struggles to maintain idle, while the transmission shifts roughly between gears. Externally, the body shows heavy rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively. The interior has seen better days, with multiple tears in the seating and a non-functional climate control system. This is strictly a project car or a candidate for parts, and it is priced accordingly to reflect its current state.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
